4.dialog: Lots of good stuff today, Commander~! Don't miss out, *Nyaa~*!

6.dialog: {namecode:98} is busy, *Nyaa~*, and doesn't have time to play with Commander, *Nyaa~*...

7.dialog: Do you want to be 'repaired' by {namecode:98}, Commander?

8.dialog: *Nyaa~*?! Commander... you want to buy something, *Nyaa~*?

11.dialog: It'd make {namecode:98} happy if you took a look at something to buy... *Nyaa~*...

13.dialog: Watch out for weird gear, you might get hurt, *Nyaa~*!

15.dialog: *Purr*, *Nyaa~*? Commander, touching fish again, *Nyaa~*? Buy something or I'm going to report you, *Nyaa~*!

18.dialog: Come and see me when you can, *Nyaa~*!

19.dialog: Commander, what's up? Want {namecode:98} to inspect you?

21.dialog: Well... it's not like you get a discount, *Nyaa~*!

22.dialog: *Nyaa...~* Ha!! So, so comfortable. You almost got away with it, *Nyaa~*!
